data.title: Great Little Shop
data.text: We were staying on Englewood Beach and went out to get bait at 6pm on a Wednesday to do some night fishing. Turns out all the bait shops close at 6! Made a phone call to Fine Bait and Tackle and the gentleman there stayed open almost an hour after closing time to sell us bait. Great little shop with everything you need for fresh water fishing in the river or saltwater fishing in the gulf!

data.title: hometown service and great bait shop
data.text: very friendly service and a great selection of fishing tackle and supplies...great prices and friendly people

data.title: Good place for your fishing needs
data.text: The only problem with this place is they are out of live shrimp often. When I have been able to get shrimp it was reasonable
